---
title: Zucchini & Parmesan-Crusted Chicken with Mashed Potatoes and Green Beans
description: Topping chicken with grated zucchini may sound odd, but it keeps chicken moist and tender in the oven. A bit of parmesan cheese adds a nutty flavor to the mix. Creamy mashed potatoes and green beans are a classic accompaniment.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56d5c2934dab713e7e8b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/56d5c2934dab713e7e8b4567.pdf
author: Michelle Doll Olson
course: main course
time required: 30 minutes
